text: Majeed Ali (born 1 July 1944) is a former Iraqi football defender who played for Iraq in the 1972 AFC Asian Cup. He played for the national team between 1970 and 1972. ==References== Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:1972 AFC Asian Cup players Category:Possibly living people Category:Association football defenders Category:1944 births
